Rate Measurement Test Protocol Problem
Statement and Requirements
2015", shape=ellipse, URL="RFC7497.html", target="_top", tooltip="This memo presents a problem statement for access rate measurement for test protocols to measure IP Performance Metrics (IPPM).  Key rate measurement test protocol aspects include the ability to control packet characteristics on the tested path, such as asymmetric rate and asymmetric packet size."];
  cites -> RFC7497;
