A One-Way Loss Metric for IP Performance
Metrics (IPPM)
2016", shape=ellipse, URL="RFC7680.html", target="_top", tooltip="This memo defines a metric for one-way loss of packets across Internet paths.  It builds on notions introduced and discussed in the IP Performance Metrics (IPPM) Framework document, RFC 2330; the reader is assumed to be familiar with that document.  This memo makes RFC 2680 obsolete."];
  cites -> RFC7680;
